00:21:37.884 --> 00:21:39.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But who cares about facts?

463
00:21:40.310 --> 00:21:42.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The chronicle says that you have
