00:21:49.507 --> 00:21:52.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Continue with the saga.

466
00:21:52.706 --> 00:21:54.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My pleasure.

