605
00:28:37.605 --> 00:28:37.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jadzia

606
00:28:38.203 --> 00:28:39.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
we need to...

607
00:28:43.595 --> 00:28:44.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're mad.

608
00:28:44.363 --> 00:28:47.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am concerned.

609
00:28:47.082 --> 00:28:49.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, well, I'm hung over.

610
00:28:49.442 --> 00:28:50.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Can we talk later?

611
00:28:50.781 --> 00:28:52.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We have a very
serious problem.

612
00:28:52.851 --> 00:28:54.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sirella has canceled
the wedding.

613
00:28:55.820 --> 00:28:57.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She doesn't waste
any time, does she?

614
00:28:58.158 --> 00:28:59.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She said
you attacked her.

615
00:29:01.617 --> 00:29:02.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She pulled a knife.

616
00:29:07.975 --> 00:29:09.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You are forbidden to join
the House of Martok.

617
00:29:10.795 --> 00:29:12.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So I won't be invited
to the family picnics.

618
00:29:13.395 --> 00:29:15.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll live.

619
00:29:15.234 --> 00:29:17.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I cannot believe
how you're taking this so lightly.

620
00:29:17.873 --> 00:29:19.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do you hear that?

621
00:29:19.073 --> 00:29:20.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

622
00:29:20.512 --> 00:29:21.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>muffled voices </i>)

623
00:29:21.912 --> 00:29:23.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It sounds like voices.

624
00:29:29.270 --> 00:29:30.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hi.
-Hi.

625
00:29:30.669 --> 00:29:32.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ODO:
Is the party over?

626
00:29:32.749 --> 00:29:36.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You could say that.
It's 10:30.

627
00:29:36.068 --> 00:29:37.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
In the morning?
I'm on duty.

628
00:29:38.547 --> 00:29:40.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So am I.

629
00:29:40.107 --> 00:29:41.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It was a great party.

630
00:29:41.226 --> 00:29:42.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thanks.

631
00:29:48.743 --> 00:29:50.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We must deal
with the situation now.

632
00:29:50.942 --> 00:29:53.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Stop yelling.
My head hurts.

633
00:29:54.521 --> 00:29:57.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You must go to Sirella
and beg her forgiveness.

634
00:30:04.398 --> 00:30:06.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I don't beg.

635
00:30:06.518 --> 00:30:09.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You are allowing
your pride to blind you.

636
00:30:09.775 --> 00:30:10.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Look who's talking.

637
00:30:11.138 --> 00:30:12.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You want me to go crawling
to some old hag

638
00:30:12.857 --> 00:30:15.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
just so you can have your
traditional Klingon wedding.

639
00:30:15.075 --> 00:30:17.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This is about more
than just tradition.

640
00:30:20.315 --> 00:30:22.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You and I have embarked
on a spiritual journey,

641
00:30:23.233 --> 00:30:24.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
one that will
bind us together

642
00:30:24.694 --> 00:30:26.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
through this life
and into the next.

643
00:30:26.564 --> 00:30:27.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You cannot turn back now.

644
00:30:27.685 --> 00:30:26.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Maybe you're on
a spiritual journey, Worf,

645
00:30:30.204 --> 00:30:32.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but I just want
to get married.

646
00:30:33.291 --> 00:30:36.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So why don't you go back
to sweating and bleeding

647
00:30:36.413 --> 00:30:37.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
with your friends
in the holosuite,

648
00:30:38.148 --> 00:30:39.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and when you're done,

649
00:30:39.428 --> 00:30:40.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
meet me in
Benjamin's office

650
00:30:41.227 --> 00:30:42.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and he'll perform
the ceremony.

651
00:30:51.266 --> 00:30:52.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If that is your attitude...

652
00:30:55.023 --> 00:30:56.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
perhaps Sirella
was right about you.

653
00:31:00.703 --> 00:31:02.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There should be no wedding.

654
00:31:04.907 --> 00:31:05.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's fine with me.

655
00:31:08.740 --> 00:31:10.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>door opens, closes </i>)

656
00:31:24.775 --> 00:31:28.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>whistling </i>)

657
00:31:28.774 --> 00:31:30.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What's going on?

658
00:31:30.432 --> 00:31:31.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Haven't you heard?

659
00:31:31.825 --> 00:31:32.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The wedding's off.

660
00:31:32.253 --> 00:31:33.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Off? Why?

661
00:31:33.892 --> 00:31:37.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She says it's because
he's a pig-headed, stubborn man

662
00:31:37.464 --> 00:31:39.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who puts tradition
before everything else.

663
00:31:39.849 --> 00:31:42.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He says it's because
she's a frivolous

664
00:31:42.450 --> 00:31:43.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
emotional woman

665
00:31:43.650 --> 00:31:46.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who refuses to take him
or his culture seriously.

666
00:31:47.067 --> 00:31:47.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You can see
the problem.

667
00:31:49.267 --> 00:31:50.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They're both right.

668
00:31:51.070 --> 00:31:52.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Exactly.

669
00:31:52.106 --> 00:31:55.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well... there's only
one thing for it.

670
00:31:56.425 --> 00:31:58.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dinner.

671
00:31:58.544 --> 00:32:00.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll get the menu.

672
00:32:08.381 --> 00:32:09.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>door chimes </i>)

673
00:32:09.901 --> 00:32:11.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Enter.

674
00:32:18.018 --> 00:32:20.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Worf...

675
00:32:20.178 --> 00:32:22.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
you've made a grave error.

676
00:32:24.297 --> 00:32:26.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Perhaps.

677
00:32:27.056 --> 00:32:29.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do you still love her?

678
00:32:29.295 --> 00:32:31.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Of course.

679
00:32:31.254 --> 00:32:33.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
However, in this
case, <i>that...</i>

680
00:32:33.814 --> 00:32:35.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
may not be enough.

681
00:32:37.512 --> 00:32:39.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Anyone can see that we are
hopelessly mismatched.

682
00:32:40.451 --> 00:32:42.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She is a Trill;
I am a Klingon.

683
00:32:42.451 --> 00:32:44.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She has had
five marriages.

684
00:32:45.790 --> 00:32:47.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This would be my first.

685
00:32:48.149 --> 00:32:50.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When she is laughing,
I am somber.

686
00:32:50.648 --> 00:32:52.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When I am happy,
she is crying.

687
00:32:52.189 --> 00:32:54.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She plays <i>tongo </i>with
the Ferengi bartender.

688
00:32:55.446 --> 00:32:56.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I can barely stand him.

689
00:33:00.667 --> 00:33:03.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She mocks everything...

690
00:33:03.427 --> 00:33:04.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
while I take
everything seriously.

691
00:33:07.343 --> 00:33:09.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She is nothing like the woman
I thought I would marry.

692
00:33:12.201 --> 00:33:14.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We are not accorded
the luxury

693
00:33:14.262 --> 00:33:17.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
of choosing the women
we fall in love with.

694
00:33:18.480 --> 00:33:20.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you think Sirella
is anything like the woman

695
00:33:20.699 --> 00:33:22.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I thought that I'd marry?

696
00:33:24.178 --> 00:33:27.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She is a prideful,
arrogant, mercurial woman

697
00:33:29.748 --> 00:33:33.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who shares my bed far too
infrequently for my taste.

698
00:33:35.155 --> 00:33:35.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And yet...

699
00:33:38.234 --> 00:33:39.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I love her...

700
00:33:40.213 --> 00:33:40.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
deeply.

701
00:33:42.212 --> 00:33:44.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm.

702
00:33:44.092 --> 00:33:48.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We Klingons often tout our...

703
00:33:48.410 --> 00:33:49.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
prowess in battle...

704
00:33:50.750 --> 00:33:54.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
our desire for glory and honor
above all else...

705
00:33:56.069 --> 00:33:58.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but how hollow is
the sound of victory...

706
00:33:59.388 --> 00:34:02.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
without someone
to share it with?

707
00:34:02.875 --> 00:34:05.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Honor gives
little comfort

708
00:34:05.133 --> 00:34:06.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
to a man alone
in his home...

709
00:34:08.386 --> 00:34:10.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and in his heart.

710
00:34:16.464 --> 00:34:18.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
One steak with mushrooms

711
00:34:18.352 --> 00:34:19.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
baked potato, sour cream
and chives.

712
00:34:19.822 --> 00:34:21.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I should have had that.

713
00:34:21.303 --> 00:34:24.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
One double Altair sandwich,
no mustard...

714
00:34:24.501 --> 00:34:26.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
two bowls of linguini,

715
00:34:26.301 --> 00:34:29.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bajoran shrimp
with extra cheese.

716
00:34:30.117 --> 00:34:31.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
One loaf of mapa bread.

717
00:34:31.739 --> 00:34:33.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Quark, where's
the <i>kava </i>juice?

718
00:34:33.538 --> 00:34:34.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They're still
squeezing the roots

719
00:34:34.698 --> 00:34:36.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
unless you want replicated.

720
00:34:36.693 --> 00:34:37.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We'll wait.

721
00:34:37.458 --> 00:34:38.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
SISKO:
What do you think you're doing?

722
00:34:39.415 --> 00:34:40.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The wedding's
been called off.

723
00:34:40.516 --> 00:34:41.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's back on.

724
00:34:41.676 --> 00:34:44.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf is apologizing
to Jadzia

725
00:34:44.350 --> 00:34:45.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
at this very moment.

726
00:34:45.334 --> 00:34:46.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Quark, take
it all away.

727
00:34:46.554 --> 00:34:48.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No food for those
on the path to <i>Kal'Hyah.</i>

728
00:34:49.633 --> 00:34:52.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No refunds for those on the path
to <i>Kal'Hyah </i>as well.

729
00:34:52.572 --> 00:34:52.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sorry.

730
00:34:58.450 --> 00:35:00.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Father, what happened?

731
00:35:03.209 --> 00:35:04.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She refused
to change her mind

732
00:35:05.170 --> 00:35:06.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and the wedding is still off.

733
00:35:07.249 --> 00:35:09.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>sighs </i>)

734
00:35:09.135 --> 00:35:09.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Where is she?

735
00:35:10.107 --> 00:35:10.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
In her quarters.

736
00:35:10.867 --> 00:35:12.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll go talk to her.

737
00:35:13.486 --> 00:35:15.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Just... keep them away
from the food?

738
00:35:23.443 --> 00:35:24.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>door chimes </i>)

739
00:35:24.522 --> 00:35:25.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Come in!

740
00:35:27.521 --> 00:35:28.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Save your breath.

741
00:35:28.761 --> 00:35:30.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf's gone too far,
and now it's over.

742
00:35:31.040 --> 00:35:32.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you know what
he wanted me to do?

743
00:35:33.080 --> 00:35:36.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He wanted me to go crawling
on my hands and knees to Sirella

744
00:35:36.158 --> 00:35:37.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
to beg her forgiveness.

745
00:35:37.598 --> 00:35:38.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Beg her! Me!

746
00:35:38.997 --> 00:35:40.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I was once

747
00:35:40.677 --> 00:35:43.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the Federation Ambassador
to the Klingon Empire.

748
00:35:45.896 --> 00:35:47.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I negotiated
the Khitomer Accords

749
00:35:47.677 --> 00:35:49.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
before Worf
was even born.

750
00:35:49.201 --> 00:35:50.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Curzon negotiated the Accords!

751
00:35:51.030 --> 00:35:52.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And I've got news for you,
old man.

752
00:35:52.554 --> 00:35:54.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're not Curzon anymore.

753
00:35:54.573 --> 00:35:56.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And what the hell is that
supposed to mean?

754
00:35:56.933 --> 00:35:58.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It means that you
can't expect Sirella

755
00:35:58.492 --> 00:35:59.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
to treat you like Curzon

756
00:35:59.751 --> 00:36:01.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
just because you carry
his memories.

757
00:36:01.810 --> 00:36:03.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
To her, you're just
a young woman

758
00:36:03.211 --> 00:36:05.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who decided to marry
into her family.

759
00:36:05.570 --> 00:36:07.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If it means
you have to bow down

760
00:36:07.551 --> 00:36:08.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and kiss her boots,

761
00:36:08.648 --> 00:36:11.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
that's exactly what you have
to do, and you knew that.

762
00:36:11.968 --> 00:36:13.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The moment you decided
to marry Worf,

763
00:36:13.766 --> 00:36:15.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you knew that sooner or later
you'd have to bow down

764
00:36:15.967 --> 00:36:18.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and show her the respect
that she's due.

765
00:36:18.566 --> 00:36:20.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This is Worf's fault--

766
00:36:20.165 --> 00:36:22.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf and his traditional
Klingon wedding.

767
00:36:23.099 --> 00:36:25.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, he may have let
this wedding business

768
00:36:25.125 --> 00:36:28.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
go to his head,
but you are 356 years old.

769
00:36:29.075 --> 00:36:31.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Compared to you,
Worf is just a kid.

770
00:36:32.022 --> 00:36:34.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And if you can't abide
by Klingon traditions,

771
00:36:34.861 --> 00:36:36.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
then you never should
have let yourself

772
00:36:36.302 --> 00:36:38.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
fall in love with him
in the first place.

773
00:36:40.660 --> 00:36:43.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And you <i>are</i>
in love with him.

774
00:36:46.578 --> 00:36:48.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I wasn't looking
to fall in love.

775
00:36:48.537 --> 00:36:50.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I was perfectly happy
by myself.

776
00:36:51.376 --> 00:36:54.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I had friends, a career,
adventure...

777
00:36:57.214 --> 00:37:00.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Then one day...

778
00:37:00.334 --> 00:37:02.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
this Klingon
with a bad attitude

779
00:37:02.825 --> 00:37:03.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
walked into my life

780
00:37:05.132 --> 00:37:08.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and the next thing I know,
I'm getting married.

781
00:37:09.031 --> 00:37:12.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
After 356 years
and seven lifetimes...

782
00:37:14.309 --> 00:37:15.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I still lead with my heart.

783
00:37:16.608 --> 00:37:19.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You know, that is
what I've always loved about you.

784
00:37:22.727 --> 00:37:24.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And I think that's why
Worf loves you, too.

785
00:37:31.124 --> 00:37:34.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>sighs </i>)

786
00:37:34.743 --> 00:37:38.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Whatever happened to that
young, callow Ensign I used to know?

787
00:37:40.682 --> 00:37:42.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The one who used
to turn to me

788
00:37:42.801 --> 00:37:44.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
for advice all the time?

789
00:37:45.280 --> 00:37:48.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You know,
the one with hair?

790
00:37:49.800 --> 00:37:50.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I grew up.

791
00:37:55.718 --> 00:37:58.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I guess it's time
I grow up, too.

792
00:37:58.677 --> 00:38:00.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mmm.

793
00:38:38.704 --> 00:38:40.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
With fire and steel

794
00:38:40.943 --> 00:38:43.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
did the gods forge
the Klingon heart.

795
00:38:44.402 --> 00:38:46.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So fiercely did it beat,

796
00:38:46.458 --> 00:38:50.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so loud was the sound,
that the gods cried out,

797
00:38:50.061 --> 00:38:52.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"On this day
we have brought forth

798
00:38:52.580 --> 00:38:55.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"the strongest heart
in all the heavens.

799
00:38:56.499 --> 00:38:59.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"None can stand before it
without trembling

800
00:38:59.817 --> 00:39:01.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
at its strength."

801
00:39:01.317 --> 00:39:03.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But then the Klingon heart
weakened

802
00:39:04.176 --> 00:39:07.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
its steady rhythm faltered
and the gods said,

803
00:39:07.116 --> 00:39:08.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Why have you weakened so?

804
00:39:08.995 --> 00:39:10.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"We have made you the strongest

805
00:39:10.896 --> 00:39:12.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
in all of creation."

806
00:39:13.753 --> 00:39:15.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And the heart said...

807
00:39:15.553 --> 00:39:16.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am alone.

808
00:39:18.472 --> 00:39:20.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And the gods knew
that they had erred.

809
00:39:20.771 --> 00:39:22.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So they went back
to their forge

810
00:39:22.492 --> 00:39:25.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and brought forth...
another heart.

811
00:39:53.415 --> 00:39:56.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But the second heart
beat stronger than the first,

812
00:39:57.421 --> 00:39:59.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and the first was jealous
of its power.

813
00:40:04.218 --> 00:40:05.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Fortunately...

814
00:40:06.458 --> 00:40:07.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the second heart
was tempered

815
00:40:07.818 --> 00:40:08.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
by wisdom.

816
00:40:09.517 --> 00:40:12.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If we join together,
no force can stop us.

817
00:40:20.033 --> 00:40:22.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And when the two hearts
began to beat together,

818
00:40:23.612 --> 00:40:26.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
they filled the heavens
with a terrible sound.

819
00:40:27.451 --> 00:40:31.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
For the first time,
the gods knew fear.

820
00:40:31.331 --> 00:40:33.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They tried to flee,
but it was too late.

821
00:40:34.030 --> 00:40:36.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The Klingon hearts
destroyed the gods

822
00:40:36.832 --> 00:40:37.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
who created them

823
00:40:38.048 --> 00:40:40.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and turned the heavens
to ashes.

824
00:40:41.187 --> 00:40:42.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
To this very day

825
00:40:43.091 --> 00:40:47.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
no one can oppose the beating
of two Klingon hearts.

826
00:40:49.684 --> 00:40:51.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not even me.

827
00:40:55.203 --> 00:40:59.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf, son of Mogh,
does your heart beat

828
00:40:59.202 --> 00:41:01.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
only for this woman?

829
00:41:01.361 --> 00:41:03.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

830
00:41:04.680 --> 00:41:06.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And will you swear
to join with her

831
00:41:06.879 --> 00:41:09.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and stand with her
against all who oppose you?

832
00:41:10.489 --> 00:41:12.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I swear.

833
00:41:12.478 --> 00:41:15.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jadzia, daughter of Kela,

834
00:41:15.637 --> 00:41:18.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
does your heart beat
only for this man?

835
00:41:19.316 --> 00:41:21.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

836
00:41:21.236 --> 00:41:23.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And do you swear
to join with him

837
00:41:23.202 --> 00:41:23.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and stand with him

838
00:41:24.015 --> 00:41:25.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
against all
who would oppose you?

839
00:41:27.014 --> 00:41:28.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
( <i>whispering </i>):
I swear.

840
00:41:30.273 --> 00:41:32.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Then let all present
here today know

841
00:41:32.831 --> 00:41:36.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
that this man
and this woman are married.

842
00:41:37.430 --> 00:41:39.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>applause </i>)

843
00:41:44.788 --> 00:41:46.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now?

844
00:41:46.697 --> 00:41:47.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not yet.

845
00:41:54.985 --> 00:41:55.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now?

846
00:41:55.945 --> 00:41:57.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Patience.

847
00:42:00.083 --> 00:42:00.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My Lady.

848
00:42:02.902 --> 00:42:04.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Welcome to the House
of Martok...

849
00:42:06.501 --> 00:42:08.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
my daughter.

850
00:42:12.460 --> 00:42:13.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now, Doctor!

851
00:42:14.019 --> 00:42:16.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>yelling </i>)

